flowchart TB
    WMC[OBJ_WorldMapController Init] --> InitRoom[worldmap_InitRoom]
    InitRoom --> Sync[worldmap_SyncMarkersFromRoom]
    Sync --> EM[OBJ_EventMarker instances get event_id]

    PM[OBJ_PlayerMarker Step] --> Move[worldmap_PlayerMovementStep snap]
    PM --> E[worldmap_TryPlayerInteract]
    E --> Trigger[eventmarker_trigger]
    Trigger --> Pre{pre dialog once?}
    Pre -->|first clear| Dialog[dialog_Start]
    Pre -->|replay| Battle[worldmap_LaunchEventBattle]
    Dialog --> Battle
    Battle --> RB[Room_battle]
    RB --> Win[worldmap_ReturnToMapAfterVictory]
    Win --> Spawn[worldmap_ApplyPendingPlayerSpawn]

